Hi, 

A void function in a package is not accepted. 
See example below:

package p3;
   function int p3_func (int x); 
      p3_func = x+30+3;
   endfunction

   function void p3_msg(string s);
	$display("p3_msg:%s", s);
   endfunction
endpackage

module icarus_tb;
	int a;

	initial
	begin
		a = p3::p3_func(10);     // This is working fine
		p3::p3_msg("Hello");    // This fails to be compiled (malformed statement)
		#10;
		$finish;
	end
endmodule
